Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:24.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯萝伊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:26.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:30.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一直好想见你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:32.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:34.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这几位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:38.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  托尔大人  伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:39.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:43.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你好  你就是小林啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:47.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好了好了  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:49.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:51.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:55.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你们几个  乱跑步很危险的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:56.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,知道了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,-----OP-----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:31.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:33.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,从美国明尼苏达州来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:34.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明尼苏达？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:36.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是什么  好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:38.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,果然会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我说  托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么了  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:46.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么柯萝伊能流畅地说日语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:49.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为我给她施加了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:51.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,果然是这样啊  不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,说起来我们现在是要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:56.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,去秋叶原
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,秋叶原？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:57.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:00.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,按照小林你的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:02.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我准备了完美的招待计划
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:13.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,快看  我们在海面上行驶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:27.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我找来了熟悉这一带的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,直接就甩给别人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:32.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,既然是托尔的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:34.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我当然很乐于接受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也要谢谢法夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:37.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不要这么叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:38.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那些人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她有这么多朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:45.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这就是VR游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我一直很想试试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:56.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,傻站着干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:57.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,快做好战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:05.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  戴上之后景色就变了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就好像真的一样  这个好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这个真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:25.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:27.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:37.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在被干掉之前  出手干掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虚张声势是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,注意那边  小怪要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:48.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这么弱的武器算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:52.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:53.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,居然敢对康娜动手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我会给你报仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,从外面看感觉还挺超现实的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只要他们开心就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,{\c&H324C54&\bord0\frz357.2\pos(974.667,336.81)}扭蛋会馆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我认为小孩子可能会觉得这边比较有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:13.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林小林  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H61363B&\fs50\pos(1020.428,219.428)}大家原{\c&HB457B6&\fs80}来{\c&H945B3E&}都{\c&HB9A26E&}是{\c&H3DA150&}龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:16.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,居然穿着人类的衣服打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:19.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这些家伙就没有身为龙族的骄傲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你没资格说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想送给阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.59,Kobayashi S2 - Screen 2,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H552342&\pos(935.111,206.111)}胸中有丘壑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:30.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,直奔消费者们的性欲而来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么啦  你有什么意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.10,Kobayashi S2 - Screen 8,,0,0,0,,{\c&H59554D&\3c&HC7CCCD&\b1\fs40\pos(639.525,349.524)}忍者道具挂件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜  这个好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:44.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好好吃的样子
Comment: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:47.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/炸昆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太慢了  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这不是艾尔玛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:56.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然拜托她会很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:58.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但提到美食家就肯定是艾尔玛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:05:59.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明是你拜托我  说话还这么不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:04.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,听好了  柯萝伊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:08.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这家伙可是日本之耻  不对  是世界之耻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:11.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你说谁是世界级的吃货啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,谁也没这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:15.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:19.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这就是日式欢喜冤家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:21.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:24.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:27.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好啦  你快点带路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你不说我也会这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:31.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可不要让我失望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你就等着大吃一惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还真是不直率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:36.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:38.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:40.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:42.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是最近很火的棉花糖店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:43.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人气很高的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:46.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你只是自己想来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:50.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然不可否认确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:51.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是比起这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:59.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也想吃那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:00.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,软绵绵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,软绵绵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么这么好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:15.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这种时候应该怎么用日语表达呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:16.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,马基亚巴库内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,马基亚巴库内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.54,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,真是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,马基亚巴库内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下一个就吃那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:35.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,连艾尔玛也跟着一起闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还真是孩子气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这么活泼也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看上去挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:48.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你这笑得让人很不舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,简直就像是一家人放假出来玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天也有点晚了  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我还想再玩会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不要让小林为难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要不要明天再来这边玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:13.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我还有想去…想介绍给你们的店铺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:16.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已经玩够了  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明天就请您一个人玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:22.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大家一起吃才会更美味不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你想把柯萝伊喂成猪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:26.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:27.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要打架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她们又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:31.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好了好了  我们走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:35.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没办法  这次就不跟你计较
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好厉害  她很清楚该怎么对付她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:43.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林最强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:47.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  明天要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯萝伊有没有想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然出去玩也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是我想了解康娜的日常生活
Comment: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/番外篇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.02,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(350,0)\pos(966.477,598.571)}日本的接待（由龙来负责）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:15.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那个女人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:26.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯萝伊  是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:27.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:30.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也可以说是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:36.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可是康娜最好的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,亲友哦  至爱亲朋那种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:41.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你和她是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:43.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我和她是在纽约认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:44.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,纽约？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:45.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什么时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:46.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,外边包养的情妇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:50.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,说起来  你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川  我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你就是才川啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:57.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我听说过你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:04.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我叫柯萝伊  可以的话和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:08.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这种亲近的感觉是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:14.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是…仔细看的话  这孩子好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而且非常听话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:21.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要我和你玩也可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的吗  我好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:27.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,关系真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好搞定的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然她不是龙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小心点  柯萝伊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,踩出界就要接受惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:40.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很熟练呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可是很擅长活动身体的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是现在还不能放松警惕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:51.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,接下来到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:59.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很好  接下来轮到柯萝伊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:12.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,挺厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:13.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:18.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已经到头了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这种时候是该结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,井盖也算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再往这边靠点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:46.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯萝伊  接受惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这算什么嘛
Comment: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:02.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/泳池开放日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这里就是我们上学的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.57,Kobayashi S2 - Screen 8,,0,0,0,,{\c&H27332F&\b1\bord3\3c&HE3F4EF&\pos(719.771,688.6)}泳\N池\N开\N放\N日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,从这里进去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在这里上课
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:10.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我坐这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:15.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜你们是一直在这里生活的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:20.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,学校里真的有泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:22.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好了  我们也去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川  柯萝伊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:40.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,去找老师借泳衣了  可能要晚一点到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:50.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,天啊  是金发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,黑船事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.30,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,注：黑船事件，指1853年美国以炮舰威逼日本打开国门的事件。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,感觉发上网必火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.96,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,异域美女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不会很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:00.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,喂你们男生  好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,敢用奇怪的眼神看的话就杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:03.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,谁看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:06.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,骗鬼呢  刚刚肯定色眯眯地看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.12,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,又没看你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯萝伊  我们去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.82,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,啥  你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:16.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我…我其实不太会游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:19.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没事  我教你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:13:59.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,去厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:04.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:09.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜  我想到一个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:18.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么样  合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,羡慕嫉妒恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天就穿成这样继续玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:25.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这里就是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:28.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么  我们玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这种的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我玩这个可是高手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:36.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,爸爸都没赢过我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:38.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,先攻  右手放在蓝色上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:42.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,后攻  左脚放在黑色上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:49.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜  能把腰再挺一挺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Comment: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/胧家小卖部
Comment: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/零食
Comment: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:57.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,Hi  伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我过来玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:02.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就等你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,昨天开始就住我们家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是柯萝伊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:08.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来自明尼苏达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯萝伊  来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:14.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明尼苏达！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,美国那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是这日语说太好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:23.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这个和…这个也要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:26.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,都是之前没见过的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:28.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是什么零食？
