Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:32.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是三颗糖里有一颗特殊的糖  超级酸的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:34.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是俄罗斯转盘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:37.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那这是…
