Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:40.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,像云朵一样软绵绵的  甜甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:42.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当我这么觉得的时候  突然就爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:43.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:46.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那个可好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:48.18,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,这里也有好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:49.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,朋友真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:52.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什么啊  你不也有朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:57.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以我就觉得挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:00.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再次认识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:06.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那个大哥哥喜欢伊露露吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,笨蛋  没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,竹人是喜欢大胸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,都说了不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:26.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你们先上房顶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:27.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:30.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,烟花  烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:34.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜  顺手把这些吃的带上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能抬起手来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:45.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:48.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我说  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:50.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:53.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林知道康娜是龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:56.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:01.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林也是龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:04.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就是个普通人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:07.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那也不是家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:10.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么会和康娜一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:12.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,顺势而为吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,和龙生活在一起是什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:19.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,像是生活在寄宿家庭里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:21.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,寄宿家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:25.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯萝伊也是差不多的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我也是龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:29.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:34.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:36.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也给我点火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:44.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:49.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯萝伊同学  我也要我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:53.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:57.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大家应该差不多要到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:17:59.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:01.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:04.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  这是啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:08.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,竹人  我也想玩烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:10.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亚小姐  晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:12.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,谢谢邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:14.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太君也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:16.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:20.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,知道了知道了  随便找个地方坐着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:23.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等等  这待遇差别太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:26.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么我们开始吧
