Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:05.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同学赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我去买新的烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:20.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜  这里还有其他龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:21.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:25.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:29.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但小林不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯萝伊开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:45.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这两天过得太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:47.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大家都是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:50.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,最喜欢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那个人的身边围着一大群龙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:02.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林是驯龙大师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:03.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大师？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:05.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对  驯龙大师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:10.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:14.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:32.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,绝对  绝对下次还要再来玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:36.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:38.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:39.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:41.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一对的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:50.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  我玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:51.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不客气  我们也玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:57.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下次离家出走就选来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:00.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就有点麻烦了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:06.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我就要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:10.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下次再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:25.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯萝伊很像托尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:28.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,哪里像了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:32.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,比如说来到一个不同文化的地方而感到迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:36.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还有会努力去了解一个人的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:42.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这么说来  那孩子也是一头龙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.18,0:21:44.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这句话我也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:54.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然后呢  我跟爸爸说了日本这边的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:56.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,他说他也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:21:59.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下次什么时候来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:01.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什么时候都欢迎你来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:03.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下次还想玩更多的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:04.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当然了
